sentence: how many flights arrive at general mitchell international
sq2:
SELECT  COUNT(*) FROM flight v0 
WHERE (v0.to_airport IN (
SELECT v1.airport_code FROM airport v1 
WHERE (v1.airport_code = 'MKE')));
sql: SELECT COUNT ( * ) FROM FLIGHT WHERE FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT WHERE AIRPORT.AIRPORT_CODE = ' MKE ' ) ;
